/* 
** About.
*/

@node ABOUTF4D "Font4D : About"
 This programm is Freeware, so do whatever you want with it,
 except earn ANY money...

 It's main purpose ( so far ) is to create animations 
 of a word, or sentence...
 ( It uses chars.inc for the font... 
        this will be enhanced in the next version )
 But you can also use it to add light, camera - movement and titles 
 to your povray scenes.

@endnode

